	measure 'Segment Share' = ```

			    DIVIDE(
			        SUM(FACT_SRE_BUILDING['Valuation (NOK)']),
			        CALCULATE(
			            SUM(FACT_SRE_BUILDING['Valuation (NOK)']),
			            REMOVEFILTERS(DIM_SRE_PROPERTY['Main Building Segment'])
			        )
			)
			```
		formatString: 0\ %;-0\ %;0\ %
		lineageTag: acce8c39-4d97-4b2b-ab63-4aac53e5e21c

		annotation PBI_FormatHint = {"isCustom":true}

	measure 'Location Share' = ```

